Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.04,0:00:51.98,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}天の下の夢幻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.20,0:00:57.14,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}花の様に儚く散っても
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.70,0:01:00.44,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}その向こうに広がってく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.76,0:01:03.04,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}果て無い世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.34,0:01:08.70,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}魂の喚びあう未来で、もう一度…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.32,0:01:11.86,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}出逢い、争って、惹かれて、
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.24,0:01:14.78,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}重なってくFEELING(Two of Hearts)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.88,0:01:17.82,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}それは高鳴った交響曲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.00,0:01:22.88,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}想いと願い一つにする…炎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.40,0:01:26.32,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}震えるHEART BEAT
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.38,0:01:29.38,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}愚かな愛の情熱を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.42,0:01:35.60,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}この時代に刻みつけて永遠に変えていこう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.72,0:01:38.80,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}誰よりも自由な心の
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.82,0:01:41.08,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}You're the only FOOL
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.26,0:01:44.52,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}胸に抱いた赤い衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.60,0:01:51.14,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}求めあうその瞳に映したのは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.32,0:01:54.90,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}「The One WORLD」
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,------------------OPCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.04,0:00:51.98,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}天空下的梦幻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.20,0:00:57.14,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}纵使飘渺如花
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.70,0:01:00.44,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}在延伸至彼方的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.76,0:01:03.04,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}那无限的世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.34,0:01:08.70,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}仍将再临灵魂彼此呼唤的尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.32,0:01:11.86,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}邂逅　争端　与迷恋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.24,0:01:14.78,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}交织其中的思绪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.88,0:01:17.82,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}谱出一支激昂的交响乐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.00,0:01:22.88,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}燃起一把融情意和祈愿为一体的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.40,0:01:26.32,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}激昂的心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.38,0:01:29.38,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}将这愚直的浓烈爱意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.42,0:01:35.60,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}镌刻到这个时代当中并使之化作永恒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.72,0:01:38.80,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}你有着自由于任何人的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.82,0:01:41.08,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}是独一无二的愚者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.26,0:01:44.52,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}胸怀赤红的冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.60,0:01:51.14,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}在彼此渴求的目光中所呈现的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.32,0:01:54.90,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}是唯一的世界
